---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Services" 
  description="Explore our acupuncture and Traditional Chinese Medicine services in Brentwood, TN. Acupuncture, cupping, moxibustion, Chinese herbs, and more."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Our Offerings</span>
      <h1>Services</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__subtitle">Traditional Chinese Medicine Treatments</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Grid -->
  <section class="services-main section section--white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="services-intro text-center">
        <p>
          At Qi For Life Acupuncture Clinic, we offer a comprehensive range of Traditional Chinese Medicine 
          treatments. Dr. Zhang selects the most appropriate methods based on your individual diagnosis and needs.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22v-7l-2-2"/><path d="M17 8v.8A6 6 0 0 1 13.8 14v0a6.5 6.5 0 0 1-3.8 1H8"/><path d="m2 2 20 20"/><path d="M12 12V2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Acupuncture</h3>
          <p>
            The foundation of Traditional Chinese Medicine, acupuncture involves the insertion of 
            fine, sterile needles at specific points to stimulate the body's natural healing processes 
            and restore balance to the flow of Qi.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13 2 3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Electronic Acupuncture</h3>
          <p>
            A modern enhancement to traditional acupuncture, electronic acupuncture adds gentle 
            electrical stimulation to the needles, intensifying the treatment for certain conditions 
            like chronic pain and muscle disorders.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"/><path d="M15.477 12.89 17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.523-9.11"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Facial & Cosmetic Acupuncture</h3>
          <p>
            A natural, non-invasive approach to facial rejuvenation that improves circulation, 
            stimulates collagen production, and promotes a healthy, youthful appearance without 
            chemicals or surgery.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22a7 7 0 0 0 7-7c0-2-1-3.9-3-5.5s-3.5-4-4-6.5c-.5 2.5-2 4.9-4 6.5C6 11.1 5 13 5 15a7 7 0 0 0 7 7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Cupping</h3>
          <p>
            Glass cups are applied to the skin using suction to remove impure energy, improve 
            circulation, and treat respiratory diseases, back pain, neck pain, and shoulder tension. 
            Some temporary marks may appear as toxins are released.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 12c2-2.96 0-7-1-8 0 3.038-1.773 4.741-3 6-1.226 1.26-2 3.24-2 5a6 6 0 1 0 12 0c0-1.532-1.056-3.94-2-5-1.786 3-2.791 3-4 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Moxibustion</h3>
          <p>
            The burning of mugwort herb near acupuncture points to strengthen blood circulation, 
            stimulate the flow of Qi, and maintain general health. This warming technique has been 
            used for thousands of years across Asia.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 3v7a6 6 0 0 0 6 6 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V3"/><path d="M4 21a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Guasa</h3>
          <p>
            A traditional therapy using a smooth-edged tool to apply pressure strokes on the skin. 
            Guasa works on the skin, blood, nervous system, and lymphatic system to boost circulation 
            and strengthen body Qi.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/><path d="M12 1v2"/><path d="M12 21v2"/><path d="M4.22 4.22l1.42 1.42"/><path d="M18.36 18.36l1.42 1.42"/><path d="M1 12h2"/><path d="M21 12h2"/><path d="M4.22 19.78l1.42-1.42"/><path d="M18.36 5.64l1.42-1.42"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>TDP Lamp</h3>
          <p>
            A therapeutic infrared mineral lamp that emits specific wavelengths to promote healing, 
            reduce inflammation, and relieve pain. Often used in conjunction with acupuncture for 
            enhanced results.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 21h10"/><path d="M12 21a9 9 0 0 0 9-9H3a9 9 0 0 0 9 9Z"/><path d="M11.38 12a2.4 2.4 0 0 1-.4-4.77 2.4 2.4 0 0 1 3.2-2.77 2.4 2.4 0 0 1 3.47-.63 2.4 2.4 0 0 1 3.37 3.37 2.4 2.4 0 0 1-1.1 3.7 2.51 2.51 0 0 1 .03 1.1"/><path d="m13 12-4.5-2"/><path d="M10.88 9.07a2.4 2.4 0 0 0-4 .5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Chinese Herbs & Consultation</h3>
          <p>
            Personalized herbal formulas are prescribed based on your unique diagnosis. These 
            time-tested remedies work synergistically with acupuncture to address the root cause 
            of health conditions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m12 3-1.912 5.813a2 2 0 0 1-1.275 1.275L3 12l5.813 1.912a2 2 0 0 1 1.275 1.275L12 21l1.912-5.813a2 2 0 0 1 1.275-1.275L21 12l-5.813-1.912a2 2 0 0 1-1.275-1.275L12 3Z"/><path d="M5 3v4"/><path d="M19 17v4"/><path d="M3 5h4"/><path d="M17 19h4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Acu-Points Hot Stone Treatment</h3>
          <p>
            Smooth, heated stones are placed on specific acupuncture points to deeply relax muscles, 
            improve circulation, and enhance the body's natural healing abilities.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4"/><path d="M12 8h.01"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Chinese Medical Qigong</h3>
          <p>
            A practice combining movement, meditation, and breathing regulation to enhance Qi flow, 
            improve blood circulation, and strengthen immune function. Dr. Zhang may recommend 
            specific exercises for home practice.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What to Expect -->
  <section class="expect section section--cream">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Your Visit</span>
        <h2>What to Expect</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="expect-content">
        <div class="expect-item">
          <h3>Initial Appointment</h3>
          <p>
            Your first visit will last approximately one hour and include a thorough consultation where 
            Dr. Zhang will diagnose and determine which TCM treatments are right for you. Using traditional 
            diagnostic methods including pulse reading and tongue diagnosis, she'll develop a personalized 
            treatment plan. Your first treatment will typically begin during this same visit.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="expect-item">
          <h3>Follow-Up Treatments</h3>
          <p>
            Follow-up visits include a shorter intake period before treatment, generally lasting 40-60 minutes. 
            The number of treatments needed depends on your age, gender, and the duration, severity, and nature 
            of your condition. Most patients feel improvement after 3-6 sessions, with significant results 
            typically seen after 10 or more treatments.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="expect-item">
          <h3>During Treatment</h3>
          <p>
            Acupuncture needles are extremely thin—about the size of a thick human hair—and produce feelings 
            such as tingling, warmth, or pressure when inserted. Many patients relax deeply or even fall asleep 
            during treatment. Needles remain in place for 20-30 minutes while you rest with soothing music in 
            a warm room.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta section section--sage">
    <div class="container container--narrow text-center">
      <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
      <p class="cta__text">
        Contact us today to schedule your first consultation and learn how Traditional Chinese Medicine 
        can help you achieve better health.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--gold">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Page Hero */
  .page-hero {
    background-color: var(--color-charcoal);
    color: var(--color-warm-white);
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0 var(--space-2xl);
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .page-hero h1 {
    color: var(--color-warm-white);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }
  
  .page-hero__subtitle {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  
  /* Services Intro */
  .services-intro {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
  }
  
  .services-intro p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-warm-gray);
  }
  
  /* Services Grid */
  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }
  
  .service-card {
    background: var(--color-cream);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: all var(--transition-medium);
  }
  
  .service-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }
  
  .service-card__icon {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-sage-light) 0%, var(--color-sage) 100%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    color: var(--color-warm-white);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  .service-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  
  .service-card p {
    color: var(--color-warm-gray);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
  
  /* What to Expect */
  .expect-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  .expect-item {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold);
    padding-left: var(--space-lg);
  }
  
  .expect-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  
  .expect-item p {
    color: var(--color-warm-gray);
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  /* CTA */
  .cta__text {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: var(--space-md) auto var(--space-xl);
  }
</style>
